      bio: `Won-Gyo recently joined the SNN Lab. She earned her B.A. in Psychology from Sungkyunkwan University and her
M.S. and Ph.D. in Cognitive Science and Brain & Cognitive Sciences from Seoul National University. She
then worked as a postdoctoral researcher at the Social Cognitive Neuroscience Lab at the University of
Chicago and the Social Neuroscience Lab at Pusan National University. Her research explores how social and
non-social resources are associated with human mind and behavior, utilizing behavioral, neuroimaging, and
social network data.`,
