    {
      name: 'Hyunseo Cho',
      title: undefined,
      metaLines: [],
      image: '/team/und_cho.jpg',
      bio: `Hyunseo Cho is a fourth-year undergraduate student double-majoring in Sociology and Computer Science at Yonsei University. She is interested in network science and computational sociology, with a focus on network brokerage, information diffusion, and longitudinal network dynamics. Her current work applies computational methods to examine how network structures such as brokerage and cohesion shape social behavior and culture. She aims to contribute to data-driven, human-centered technologies for social good at the intersection of sociology and computation.`,
